data.title: Home
data.text:
Known as the Premier Technical University of Engineering and Technology, UTHM is committed to creating a world-class environment for learning and research. UTHM is now awarded with QS 5 stars rating for internationalization, employability, online learning, research, innovation, teaching and inclusiveness. Equipped with a private airport, UTHM owns a Civil Aviation Authority Malaysia certified Flight Training Academy. As a lead university in Industry Center of Excellence for Railway, UTHM is also a hub to assist the development of human capital for the rapid expansion of Malaysian railway industry. These made UTHM as one of the top universities in Malaysia, particularly in Aerospace and Railway Engineering Technology.
